Holidays.
They bring together family and friends with
happy anticipation, regardless of distance or place
- once again being with the kind of people you
won't find anywhere else.
Your folks in Chicago. Your aunt in Bakersfield.
Your brother in Charlotte. Or a very special
friend in London.
Even though the holidays come once a year, their
memories last a lifetime. At American Airlines
and American Eagle we are working harder than
ever during this joyous season to show you how
much we appreciate your business. Our
employees are committed to bringing you the
quality service that makes your trip something
truly special in the air.
Everyone in the American Airlines and American
Eagle family is proud to be included in your
holiday travel plans. We wish you, your family
and loved ones peace and harmony throughout
the coming year.
AmericanAirlines®
Something special in the air."
